code: /**  * Return the wrapped Runnable implementation.  */ public final Runnable getDelegate() {     return this.delegate. }

comment: /**  * Delegates execution to the underlying Runnable.  */
code: /**  * Delegates execution to the underlying Runnable.  */ @Override public void run() {     this.delegate.run(). }

comment: /**  * This implementation delegates to  * {@link org.springframework.scheduling.SchedulingAwareRunnable#isLongLived()},  * if available.  */
code: /**  * This implementation delegates to  * {@link org.springframework.scheduling.SchedulingAwareRunnable#isLongLived()},  * if available.  */ @Override public boolean isDaemon() {     return (this.delegate instanceof SchedulingAwareRunnable && ((SchedulingAwareRunnable) this.delegate).isLongLived()). }

comment: /**  * This implementation is empty, since we expect the Runnable  * to terminate based on some specific shutdown signal.  */
code: /**  * This implementation is empty, since we expect the Runnable  * to terminate based on some specific shutdown signal.  */ @Override public void release() { }
